<FONT COLOR="#333399" face="Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica">If you are planning on doing the coldain shawl quests you will have to work on all of your trade skills.  I would not suggest putting all your points in tailoring though since raising it to 21 is very easy.  Just do bandages, and swatches until they are trival.<BR><BR>Put a point in tailoring, brewing and baking and the rest in blacksmithing.  </FONT><BR></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR="#e6ebd7"><TD nowrap align="left">&nbsp;</TD><TD><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td>&nbsp;&nbsp<a href="/boards/bb_profile.php?mode=view&user=160"><img src="/boards/images/profile.gif" border=0 alt="View Profile of Gildorn"></a>
