<FONT COLOR="#333399" face="Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica">For tailoring, don't bother using up training points.  Just combining 2 spider silks into a silk swatch (with guaranteed success regardless of skill) will get you up to 15.  You will reach skill 15 long before you have produced enough silk swatches to get through even cured silk, if I remember right.  For the remaining 5 points just check your local ecommons vendors who always seem to have a near limitless supply of ruined pelts for making patchwork armor.</FONT><BR></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR="#e6ebd7"><TD nowrap align="left">&nbsp;</TD><TD><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td>&nbsp;&nbsp<a href="/boards/bb_profile.php?mode=view&user=325"><img src="/boards/images/profile.gif" border=0 alt="View Profile of Palarran"></a>
