<FONT COLOR="#333399" face="Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica">I finally got to a skill of 101 in tailoring.  I am using HQ cat pelts and making reinforced masks.  Man is this expense.  So I created some twinks to get HQ pelts.<BR><BR>This also gets skills up in black smithing.<BR><BR>In regards to cost, I think I have spent close to 500pp so far.  If you are thinking about that new silk armor,  the mana part is around 7pp (poison vial 2pp and pearl 5pp) plus the cost of heady kola (2gold per bag and it takes 2 bags to make brew)  $$$$$<BR><BR>Man this skill is expensive, but worth it in the end.  Right now, I can make 10 slot bags without failures.<BR><BR>Hope to make velious items soon.<BR><BR></FONT><BR></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR="#f7f5e6"><TD nowrap align="left">&nbsp;</TD><TD><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td>&nbsp;&nbsp<a href="/boards/bb_profile.php?mode=view&user=799"><img src="/boards/images/profile.gif" border=0 alt="View Profile of Peepers"></a>
